title: WITS, Count of Armed Attacks, Middle-east and Asia, 2007- March 2008
name: WITS, Count of Armed Attacks, Middle-east and Asia, 2007- March 2008
description: This dataset shows the count of armed attacks throughout the middle east and asian countries over time. Data range is from the beginning of 2007 to the March of 2008. This data only counts the number of attacks, not the severity or success of any attacks.
